## Get Contact Information

П÷▄░ **Public** Б─■ no auth required

**Response `200`:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "email": "support@smartfix.app",
    "phone": "+20-100-000-0000",
    "social": {
      "facebook": "https://facebook.com/smartfix",
      "instagram": "https://instagram.com/smartfix",
      "twitter": "https://twitter.com/smartfix"
    }
  }
}
```

## Get technician available time slots

П÷■▓ **Protected**

Returns available 2-hour time slots for the next 7 days (8 AM to 6 PM).

**URL Param:** `:id` Б─■ technician's user `_id`

**Response `200`:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "date": "Mon Jun 10 2026",
      "slots": [
        { "time": "2026-06-10T08:00:00.000Z", "available": true },
        { "time": "2026-06-10T10:00:00.000Z", "available": true }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

## Get booking invoice

П÷■▓ **Protected** | Accessible to both customer and technician

Returns the invoice for a booking including service breakdown and payment status.

**Response `200`:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "booking": { "id": "...", "service": {...}, "scheduledAt": "...", "status": "completed" },
    "invoice": {
      "amount": 30,
      "breakdown": [{ "label": "Fix Leak", "amount": 30 }]
    },
    "payment": { "status": "success", "method": "card", "gatewayRef": "..." }
  }
}
```

